WEBVTT

00:00:08.170 --> 00:00:10.640
It'll probably take you a while to regret coming here.

00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:12.330
I wanted to kill them

00:00:13.450 --> 00:00:15.250
Whenever I saw them—murderers.

00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:19.180
Re-investigate it personally,

00:00:17.490 --> 00:00:19.160
[Lee Gilyoung]

00:00:19.740 --> 00:00:21.270
The case where Kang Woosung

00:00:21.780 --> 00:00:23.440
Was murdered by Lee Gilyoung.

00:00:26.330 --> 00:00:28.790
As a murderer's son, how dare you say you respect me?

00:00:28.790 --> 00:00:32.520
I loathe you with every fiber of my being because you are Lee Chaeha.

00:00:36.980 --> 00:00:38.360
Please listen to me.

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:39.790
Listen to what?

00:00:40.690 --> 00:00:43.290
Is there anything else I don't know, Mr. Ju?

00:00:45.510 --> 00:00:48.380
No, Mr. Kang Taeseon.

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:50.820
It's not like that.

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:52.910
I asked you.

00:00:53.570 --> 00:00:56.590
I asked why you were so obsessed with this case.

00:00:57.020 --> 00:00:59.330
What a joke I must've seemed to you.

00:00:59.450 --> 00:01:01.260
What sex partner?

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:02.620
What truth?

00:01:02.770 --> 00:01:05.360
You lured me in by suggesting Lee Gilyoung's innocence,

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:09.160
So you could toy with my heart, use me, and then trash me aside, right?

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:11.620
The closer I got to you,

00:01:11.740 --> 00:01:13.870
The harder it was for me to tell you.

00:01:14.010 --> 00:01:16.850
Because I knew it'd ruin our relationship.

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:21.360
Is there even a relationship to ruin?

00:01:23.039 --> 00:01:25.750
We were already broken when we met.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.000
Are you really going to be like this?

00:01:29.390 --> 00:01:32.030
I can't pick at my wounds

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:34.530
Just because your feelings are hurt.

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:37.220
But you ripped open my wounds.

00:01:38.520 --> 00:01:39.720
Let's talk inside...

00:01:39.850 --> 00:01:41.170
No!

00:01:47.420 --> 00:01:48.500
Lee Chaeha.

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:55.060
I was going to tell you later.

00:01:55.340 --> 00:01:56.850
Once the case is solved,

00:01:56.960 --> 00:01:59.020
Once your father's proven innocent.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.440
What if he's guilty?

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:02.590
Then what were you planning to do?

00:02:03.210 --> 00:02:07.210
Keep secretly laughing at how stupidly oblivious I am, clinging to you?

00:02:07.430 --> 00:02:11.280
Or dump me without a word of explanation?

00:02:11.890 --> 00:02:14.220
Either way, you'd get your revenge.

00:02:15.110 --> 00:02:16.430
Yes,

00:02:16.610 --> 00:02:18.340
I thought about revenge,

00:02:18.530 --> 00:02:21.260
But I couldn't do anything!

00:02:21.410 --> 00:02:22.770
Because you were...

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:27.180
Already miserable enough.

00:02:28.730 --> 00:02:30.370
Don't be disappointed.

00:02:31.130 --> 00:02:35.040
Thanks to you, I'm now more miserable than ever.

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:38.980
Chaeha, I'm sorry.

00:02:41.410 --> 00:02:43.190
I was wrong.

00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:48.920
I'm sorry

00:02:49.730 --> 00:02:53.260
You had to suffer because of my father.

00:02:53.980 --> 00:02:55.960
We don't know for sure yet.

00:02:56.940 --> 00:02:59.530
Are you saying this to get under my skin?

00:02:59.810 --> 00:03:00.900
No,

00:03:01.450 --> 00:03:03.040
I mean it.

00:03:04.090 --> 00:03:07.620
I've been wanting to ask for forgiveness on behalf of my father.

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:13.450
I'm sorry I didn't go looking for you, and I'm sorry I didn't recognize you.

00:03:14.590 --> 00:03:17.210
Chaeha, look at me.

00:03:18.570 --> 00:03:22.130
As long as I'm around you, you'll always be miserable.

00:03:22.730 --> 00:03:24.050
Because of my dad—

00:03:24.160 --> 00:03:28.880
No—because of Lee Gilyoung, your life's been a living hell.

00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:42.320
That applies to you too.

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:46.800
So let's find a way out together.

00:03:53.590 --> 00:03:55.240
Let's get out of this hell.

00:04:01.980 --> 00:04:03.560
I feel miserable.

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:07.410
Now, just looking at your face

00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:10.220
Makes me feel wretched and miserable.

00:04:12.550 --> 00:04:14.320
Is this what you want?

00:04:44.700 --> 00:04:45.720
Why?

00:04:45.930 --> 00:04:48.540
Why are you so obsessed with this case?

00:04:49.050 --> 00:04:51.640
The truth. Because I want the truth.

00:04:51.780 --> 00:04:53.280
What truth?

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:55.600
To resent you and your father,

00:04:55.730 --> 00:04:59.659
I should at least be certain of the truth.

00:05:00.620 --> 00:05:02.570
Aren't you curious?

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:05.850
Don't you want the truth?

00:05:30.930 --> 00:05:33.180
[Park Siwoo]

00:05:35.590 --> 00:05:38.720
[Kim Yoonsik]

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:45.040
[Kwak Seunghwan: because of property division?]

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:47.300
[Kim (Koryoin): drug overdose]

00:05:47.630 --> 00:05:49.150
[Found in a small room on the second floor]

00:05:49.390 --> 00:05:51.400
[Last abandoned mine in Danhyeon to be converted into a casino...]

00:05:51.970 --> 00:05:54.159
[Danhyeon Land construction led by Ohsong: casino, hotel, theme park, resort...]

00:05:54.400 --> 00:05:56.550
[First female executive in the casino industry...]

00:05:56.550 --> 00:05:58.710
[Promises "transparent management and regional win-win"]

00:05:58.870 --> 00:06:00.550
[Danhyeon City "Casino Owner Murdered"; his driver, Lee, a suspect]

00:06:07.090 --> 00:06:09.430
[The Prosecutor's Proposal]

00:06:09.500 --> 00:06:12.400
[Prosecutor's Office]

00:06:12.510 --> 00:06:14.530
[Evidence Room]

00:06:26.740 --> 00:06:27.000
[Prosecutor in charge:] [Search]

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:27.700
[Prosecutor in charge: Tak] [Search]

00:06:27.700 --> 00:06:28.440
[Prosecutor in charge: Tak Sung] [Search]

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:29.820
[Prosecutor in charge: Tak Sungwoong] [Search]

00:06:47.020 --> 00:06:48.270
Mr. Lee!

00:06:54.060 --> 00:06:55.290
Are you okay?

00:06:55.460 --> 00:06:56.659
I heard you were sick.

00:06:56.790 --> 00:06:59.330
I was so worried. Why's your phone off?

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:01.740
Sorry.

00:07:03.790 --> 00:07:05.770
Especially when things are so busy...

00:07:05.770 --> 00:07:07.250
Let me see.

00:07:08.370 --> 00:07:09.980
You have a really high fever.

00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:14.040
Here. Porridge, along with some vitamins.

00:07:14.360 --> 00:07:16.010
Remember to eat it.

00:07:16.660 --> 00:07:18.880
Thank you, Mr. Song.

00:07:19.080 --> 00:07:21.480
Just take tomorrow off too and get some rest.

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:22.450
Leave your phone off.

00:07:22.450 --> 00:07:23.640
Got it?

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:29.670
I'm off.

00:07:31.330 --> 00:07:33.340
-Mr. Song. -Yes?

00:07:34.600 --> 00:07:36.780
Um, Mr. Ju...

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:38.260
[Granny Park awl murder case]

00:07:38.260 --> 00:07:39.159
[2019 First-Instance Criminal Collegiate Case No. 294019] [Found Guilty]

00:07:39.159 --> 00:07:40.970
[Suspect's phone x1, awl x1, bag x1, blood-stained shirt x1]

00:07:54.530 --> 00:07:56.820
[General anesthetic, SEVOFLU] [1 box: 5 ml, 4 bottles]

00:07:57.500 --> 00:07:58.840
Anesthetics...

00:08:02.190 --> 00:08:03.390
[2017 Prosecution Case No. 345781]

00:08:05.910 --> 00:08:07.210
[2017 Prosecution Case No. 345781]

00:08:33.270 --> 00:08:34.409
[Shim Taehyung (forensic pathologist, National Forensic Service)]

00:08:36.929 --> 00:08:38.010
Hello,

00:08:38.190 --> 00:08:41.289
I'm Prosecutor Ju Taeseon of Criminal Div. 1, West District Office.

00:08:41.289 --> 00:08:43.090
I just sent you a photo.

00:08:43.270 --> 00:08:45.050
Can you take a look at it?

00:08:46.610 --> 00:08:48.140
It's an anesthetic.

00:08:49.190 --> 00:08:52.160
Can a blood test prove a death

00:08:52.270 --> 00:08:54.020
Caused by such an anesthetic?

00:08:54.250 --> 00:08:57.420
Yes, if the blood test is done within 3 hours of death.

00:08:58.840 --> 00:09:02.010
The autopsy was conducted 12 hours after death.

00:08:59.300 --> 00:09:00.350
[Oh Jahyeon's husband, Kwak Seunghwan] [Died 16 Oct, 2019]

00:09:00.350 --> 00:09:01.820
[Cardiac arrest, no trauma, no drug detected, autopsy done 12 hours after, cremated]

00:09:02.280 --> 00:09:04.230
What about 12 hours after death?

00:09:04.470 --> 00:09:07.120
12 hours after death by anesthetic?

00:09:07.620 --> 00:09:09.510
It can't be detected then.

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:13.790
Under such circumstances, it may be concluded as death by cardiac arrest.

00:09:13.790 --> 00:09:16.630
I see. Thank you.

00:09:20.030 --> 00:09:22.700
A few days after the anesthetic went missing,

00:09:22.700 --> 00:09:23.930
[Oh Jahyeon's husband, Kwak Seunghwan] [Died 16 Oct, 2019]

00:09:22.830 --> 00:09:25.140
Oh Jahyeon’s husband died.

00:09:23.940 --> 00:09:26.430
[Cardiac arrest, no trauma, no drug detected, autopsy done 12 hours after, cremated]

00:09:26.900 --> 00:09:28.670
Three days later,

00:09:28.660 --> 00:09:29.450
[Oh Jahyeon's husband, Kwak Seunghwan] [Died 16 Oct, 2019]

00:09:28.890 --> 00:09:31.330
Her OB-GYN died.

00:09:29.500 --> 00:09:31.490
[Oh Jahyeon's OB-GYN] [Died 19 Oct, 2019]

00:09:50.780 --> 00:09:52.250
[Call Records: N/A]

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:56.000
[Messages: N/A]

00:09:57.940 --> 00:09:59.300
Darn it.

00:10:06.190 --> 00:10:07.170
Mr. Song.

00:10:07.860 --> 00:10:09.100
Yes, Mr. Ju.

00:10:10.330 --> 00:10:12.060
Did you stay up all night again?

00:10:13.740 --> 00:10:16.290
Run forensics on this phone.

00:10:17.140 --> 00:10:18.190
Oh, okay.

00:10:21.870 --> 00:10:23.580
M-Mr. Ju!

00:10:23.910 --> 00:10:26.480
Just leaving a-after tossing me this phone?

00:10:27.930 --> 00:10:31.070
Also, I'll inform them.

00:10:31.290 --> 00:10:32.870
We'll talk later.

00:10:33.090 --> 00:10:33.680
Yeah?

00:10:33.810 --> 00:10:34.720
Okay.

00:10:58.780 --> 00:11:00.880
As a last resort, my dad

00:11:01.010 --> 00:11:03.040
Sent that man abroad.

00:11:03.680 --> 00:11:05.020
Russia?

00:11:24.710 --> 00:11:25.760
You guys go ahead.

00:11:34.190 --> 00:11:35.920
[Happy Child Orphanage] [Social Worker: Hwang Minkyung]

00:12:35.230 --> 00:12:36.710
A keepsake...

00:12:45.090 --> 00:12:46.790
What are you doing over there?

00:12:58.850 --> 00:13:01.440
Hello, I'm Prosecutor Ju Taeseon of the West District Office.

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:04.900
Have you ever taken in a child by the surname of Tak?

00:13:02.270 --> 00:13:04.800
[Happy Child Orphanage] [Social Worker: Hwang Minkyung]

00:13:08.090 --> 00:13:10.140
Okay. Thank you.

00:13:10.340 --> 00:13:13.140
If you find anything, please call me immediately.

00:13:15.980 --> 00:13:18.230
If the child was abandoned upon birth,

00:13:18.390 --> 00:13:20.560
There wouldn't be any info about their parents.

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:23.530
So, usually, they'd randomly name the child

00:13:23.650 --> 00:13:25.050
To register their birth.

00:13:25.590 --> 00:13:26.780
Right.

00:13:28.100 --> 00:13:29.500
He's one of us

00:13:29.720 --> 00:13:31.840
And even a chief prosecutor.

00:13:32.010 --> 00:13:34.560
You know everyone's freaking out about it, right?

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:37.410
It's not like Mr. Tak had a good reputation to begin with.

00:13:37.410 --> 00:13:40.240
I'm starting to wonder if this is the right thing to do.

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:42.440
What about you? Found anything?

00:13:44.670 --> 00:13:47.490
You know how Soyeon was investigating

00:13:47.650 --> 00:13:51.380
The corruption scandal of Oh Jahyeon and the casino construction?

00:13:51.940 --> 00:13:55.870
I heard the director who tormented Soyeon and drove her to her death...

00:13:56.310 --> 00:13:57.710
Bloody hell.

00:13:58.370 --> 00:14:00.830
He was Tak Sungwoong's training batchmate.

00:14:03.040 --> 00:14:08.230
I think Tak Sungwoong... got him to stop Soyeon.

00:14:08.530 --> 00:14:10.220
Just to protect Oh Jahyeon. That rat.

00:14:10.220 --> 00:14:11.940
What a scoundrel.

00:14:13.230 --> 00:14:14.520
Right, also,

00:14:16.110 --> 00:14:18.840
I'm afraid Mr. Lee will face disciplinary action.

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:19.830
What?

00:14:20.210 --> 00:14:21.530
Why Mr. Lee?

00:14:22.520 --> 00:14:23.780
I heard that Mr. Lee

00:14:24.660 --> 00:14:26.420
Is Lee Gilyoung's son.

00:14:27.680 --> 00:14:31.060
The laundry company owner you asked me to investigate

00:14:31.190 --> 00:14:33.300
Was Mr. Lee's uncle.

00:14:33.850 --> 00:14:35.060
Gosh.

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:37.480
His dad's a murderer,

00:14:37.620 --> 00:14:39.590
And his uncle's in jail.

00:14:39.860 --> 00:14:42.320
Hardly a family that inspires reliability.

00:14:42.620 --> 00:14:46.450
Besides, with Tak suspended over a murder case,

00:14:46.660 --> 00:14:49.170
Putting someone from Office 512 on leave

00:14:49.300 --> 00:14:51.300
Looks better internally.

00:14:51.940 --> 00:14:52.990
But

00:14:53.520 --> 00:14:54.670
Can Lee Chaeha...

00:14:57.040 --> 00:14:58.860
Be trusted?

00:14:59.400 --> 00:15:01.010
Yoon Gyuho!

00:15:03.230 --> 00:15:04.590
Okay.

00:15:06.880 --> 00:15:08.060
Anyway,

00:15:08.400 --> 00:15:12.240
I don't think I can help with Mr. Lee.

00:15:14.330 --> 00:15:17.660
I'll request an arrest warrant for Tak Sungwoong tomorrow.

00:15:18.550 --> 00:15:19.850
Alright.

00:15:20.700 --> 00:15:23.560
If this just fizzles out now, even I'll be in danger.

00:15:23.580 --> 00:15:25.840
Well, you always go through with things.

00:15:26.730 --> 00:15:29.840
This time, you'll finish what you started too, right?

00:15:30.870 --> 00:15:32.400
I have to.

00:15:58.080 --> 00:15:59.480
Who is it?

00:16:00.530 --> 00:16:02.120
Mr. Ju?

00:16:44.710 --> 00:16:46.860
[Prosecutor Ju Taeseon]

00:16:57.180 --> 00:16:58.120
Chaeha,

00:16:58.280 --> 00:16:59.410
Is something wrong?

00:17:00.020 --> 00:17:04.730
I heard you're the only one who can convince Mr. Ju.

00:17:04.859 --> 00:17:06.640
Listen carefully.

00:17:06.829 --> 00:17:10.520
Tell him not to apply for a warrant tomorrow.

00:17:10.740 --> 00:17:12.010
Got it?

00:17:12.130 --> 00:17:14.069
Answer me if you heard me.

00:17:14.140 --> 00:17:15.240
Answer me!

00:17:18.270 --> 00:17:21.630
Is it because... of Oh Jahyeon?

00:17:32.650 --> 00:17:34.150
Wait...

00:17:38.470 --> 00:17:40.170
Turn yourself in.

00:17:43.510 --> 00:17:44.710
Turn...

00:17:49.540 --> 00:17:50.520
Chaeha!

00:17:52.390 --> 00:17:53.610
Chaeha, are you okay?

00:18:07.980 --> 00:18:09.320
Lee Chaeha...

00:18:11.480 --> 00:18:13.200
He is Lee Gilyoung's son.

00:18:17.850 --> 00:18:20.760
He's toying with you, Taeseon.

00:18:20.980 --> 00:18:24.180
You're the one who's been toying with me for over a decade.

00:18:45.880 --> 00:18:47.380
Don't tell me...

00:18:49.150 --> 00:18:50.940
You like him?

00:18:54.170 --> 00:18:55.610
Oh.

00:18:56.510 --> 00:18:58.150
It's mutual.

00:19:01.380 --> 00:19:03.140
Oh Jahyeon was right.

00:19:03.290 --> 00:19:04.660
She was right.

00:19:04.810 --> 00:19:07.250
-You bastard! -Mr. Ju!

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:16.300
Mr. Ju!

00:19:24.510 --> 00:19:25.990
Don't you feel sorry for him?

00:19:25.990 --> 00:19:28.210
How are you going to make up for ruining our lives?

00:19:28.210 --> 00:19:30.780
Say something, you bastard!

00:19:33.720 --> 00:19:35.450
If I'd known this would happen,

00:19:36.620 --> 00:19:40.770
I would've just killed both of you back then.

00:19:41.280 --> 00:19:42.540
You damn murderer!

00:19:42.690 --> 00:19:45.360
-Please! -Someone reported trespassing.

00:20:00.390 --> 00:20:01.920
Come with us to the station.

00:20:21.190 --> 00:20:22.420
Doesn't it hurt?

00:20:31.630 --> 00:20:33.450
Look who's talking.

00:20:41.730 --> 00:20:43.830
Step away from the work.

00:20:45.410 --> 00:20:46.630
What?

00:20:47.720 --> 00:20:50.020
Or transfer to another prosecutor's office.

00:20:50.020 --> 00:20:51.470
No, I don't want that.

00:20:51.640 --> 00:20:52.440
Why must I...

00:20:52.540 --> 00:20:54.590
Since I started this job...

00:20:56.740 --> 00:20:59.340
I've only made one mistake. You know what it is?

00:21:01.610 --> 00:21:04.670
I didn't expect you to become my weakness.

00:21:06.010 --> 00:21:07.600
Do you regret it?

00:21:08.430 --> 00:21:09.800
Yeah.

00:21:11.270 --> 00:21:12.870
I regret it.

00:21:14.080 --> 00:21:16.600
I regret dragging you into this.

00:21:17.330 --> 00:21:19.540
When someone messes with you,

00:21:20.870 --> 00:21:23.130
I freeze up.

00:21:24.010 --> 00:21:26.700
I get so furious, like I'm about to explode.

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:31.520
I don't regret it.

00:21:34.580 --> 00:21:36.670
Knowing you, working with you,

00:21:36.810 --> 00:21:38.800
And being with you,

00:21:38.930 --> 00:21:41.200
I don't regret any of it.

00:21:42.490 --> 00:21:45.410
Sooner or later, you'll regret saying this, right?

00:21:47.930 --> 00:21:48.870
Lee Chaeha...

00:21:50.460 --> 00:21:52.320
I'll go first.

00:21:55.140 --> 00:21:57.620
I like you.

00:21:57.670 --> 00:21:59.420
I like you a lot.

00:22:01.690 --> 00:22:04.340
That's not what I was going to say.

00:22:09.120 --> 00:22:10.900
You're right.

00:22:11.990 --> 00:22:14.390
You'll be miserable if you're with me.

00:22:16.770 --> 00:22:18.100
That's right.

00:22:19.940 --> 00:22:21.760
Staying together

00:22:23.210 --> 00:22:25.070
Might bring more misery.

00:22:25.380 --> 00:22:27.910
I thought making you miserable

00:22:28.360 --> 00:22:30.810
Was revenge.

00:22:31.160 --> 00:22:33.070
I wanted you to be as miserable—

00:22:33.220 --> 00:22:36.630
No—a million times more miserable than me.

00:22:36.940 --> 00:22:39.670
That's how it should've been.

00:22:41.800 --> 00:22:46.690
But the more miserable you are, the more miserable I am. Why?

00:22:48.930 --> 00:22:50.650
Chaeha, I'm sorry.

00:22:52.000 --> 00:22:53.870
I was wrong.

00:22:56.480 --> 00:22:59.350
I didn't want to fall for you either.

00:23:12.670 --> 00:23:14.600
Instead of being happy alone,

00:23:15.520 --> 00:23:18.380
I'd rather be miserable with you.

00:23:19.070 --> 00:23:21.010
This is my choice.

00:23:28.520 --> 00:23:29.960
Kiss me.

00:23:38.920 --> 00:23:42.070
This isn't some final goodbye, is it?

00:23:43.130 --> 00:23:44.730
You're so perceptive.

00:23:45.270 --> 00:23:47.300
That's why I appointed you.

00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:49.410
No!

00:23:49.600 --> 00:23:51.950
I mean, you can't do this.

00:23:53.150 --> 00:23:54.810
Tak Sungwoong

00:23:55.710 --> 00:23:57.230
Came to you because

00:23:57.370 --> 00:24:00.680
He knew we'd request a warrant for him tomorrow.

00:24:01.150 --> 00:24:04.250
You mean someone's leaking the info?

00:24:04.580 --> 00:24:06.790
It's either Yoon Gyuho

00:24:07.230 --> 00:24:08.970
Or Song Haneul

00:24:09.080 --> 00:24:11.440
Who leaks info to Tak Sungwoong.

00:24:11.710 --> 00:24:13.900
So, one of them is Tak's son?

00:24:14.660 --> 00:24:16.220
Maybe.

00:24:16.470 --> 00:24:17.750
Anyway,

00:24:18.360 --> 00:24:20.390
Things are about to get really dangerous.

00:24:20.390 --> 00:24:21.490
So stay out of it.

00:24:21.610 --> 00:24:22.470
I don't want to.

00:24:23.800 --> 00:24:26.010
So let's find a way out together.

00:24:27.220 --> 00:24:28.900
Let's get out of this hell.

00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:31.910
You said you want us to find a way out

00:24:32.050 --> 00:24:33.390
Of this hell together.

00:24:34.820 --> 00:24:36.010
Then,

00:24:37.640 --> 00:24:40.370
Can you make sure you stay close to my side?

00:24:40.610 --> 00:24:42.910
Can you keep yourself safe

00:24:44.150 --> 00:24:46.010
So I don't regret falling for you?

00:25:05.470 --> 00:25:06.540
Yes.

00:25:07.410 --> 00:25:08.880
I'm confident.

00:25:16.750 --> 00:25:18.880
[The Prosecutor's Proposal]

00:25:18.900 --> 00:25:22.480
[In the Next Episode]

00:25:19.220 --> 00:25:21.150
The accomplice who dumped the body

00:25:21.180 --> 00:25:23.230
Was your and Oh Jahyeon's son.

00:25:26.370 --> 00:25:27.400
Mr. Yoon.

00:25:30.010 --> 00:25:32.610
Why's your birthday different from Soyeon's?

00:25:32.650 --> 00:25:35.660
Remember the glove found near the body of Kim, the Koryoin?

00:25:35.660 --> 00:25:37.210
The DNA on it matches

00:25:37.380 --> 00:25:39.580
The DNA of your chief prosecutor's son.

00:25:39.690 --> 00:25:40.810
Who is it?

